001package edu.cnm.deepdive.leavemealone.model.entity;
002
003
004import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
005import androidx.annotation.Nullable;
006import androidx.room.ColumnInfo;
007import androidx.room.Embedded;
008import androidx.room.Entity;
009import androidx.room.Index;
010import androidx.room.PrimaryKey;
011import edu.cnm.deepdive.leavemealone.model.pojo.GPSCoord;
012import java.time.Instant;
013
014@Entity(
015    tableName = "location",
016    indices = {})
017public class Location {
018
019    @PrimaryKey(autoGenerate = true)
020    @ColumnInfo(name = "location_id")
021    private long id;
022
023    @ColumnInfo(name = "alert_id")
024    @Nullable
025    private long alertId;
026
027    @ColumnInfo(name = "secure", index = true)
028    private boolean secure;
029
030    @Embedded
031    private GPSCoord gpsCoord;
032
033    public long getId() {
034        return id;
035    }
036
037    public void setId(long id) {
038        this.id = id;
039    }
040
041    public long getAlertId() {
042        return alertId;
043    }
044
045    public void setAlertId(long alertId) {
046        this.alertId = alertId;
047    }
048
049    public boolean isSecure() {
050        return secure;
051    }
052
053    public void setSecure(boolean secure) {
054        this.secure = secure;
055    }
056
057    public GPSCoord getGpsCoord() {
058        return gpsCoord;
059    }
060
061    public void setGpsCoord(GPSCoord gpsCoord) {
062        this.gpsCoord = gpsCoord;
063    }
064}
